{"tid":1136378,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"DSE考試費連續第5年加價 語文科$644加至$670","createTime":"2019-05-03T03:24:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T04:36:54.000Z","uid":3090,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dbb431e4f9ab04752528b8edb74f879f4fbae2a4","tid":1136378,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T03:24:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SbAN8hG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSbAN8hG.png&h=8dd9de67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n政府今日刊憲，指根據《香港考試及評核局條例》，公佈調高2020年香港中學文憑試考試費，自修生報名費由$494加至$514，語文科考試就由$644加至$670，其他科目則由$431加至$448。加幅均約為4%。<br />\n<br />\n香港中學文憑試考試費已連續第5年加價。假如一名考生報考2個語文及4個非語文科目的學校考生，考試費將由今年的$3,012上升至$3,132。不過剛公佈的財政預算案宣佈，將為中學文憑試日校考生代繳考試費，令有關加幅只影響自修生考生。"},{"pid":"857991547488745838403f7eb2608ad3a80b9ebd","tid":1136378,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T03:39:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f654fa4a67cb4071515bf73927ba7eb226c17f40","tid":1136378,"uid":209487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T03:46:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b2d104fa4e679c26d68fcf541f712872073f5946","tid":1136378,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f654fa4a67cb4071515bf73927ba7eb226c17f40","tid":1136378,"uid":209487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T03:46:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T03:47:39.000Z","msg":"24分夠唔夠入共產黨"},{"pid":"38fb668ea9a1c506045db8215af49e0effd04b0d","tid":1136378,"uid":209487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T03:48:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"26c7517ed58c9f3ad3cdd29b006afb4d21caeb4f","tid":1136378,"uid":137480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2d104fa4e679c26d68fcf541f712872073f5946","tid":1136378,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f654fa4a67cb4071515bf739